knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n----------<br />\n痴線！有手足花時間搞咗呢壇嘢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1783113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1783113</a>"},{"pid":"f74cfb4160ba4918cdc7f09124859db2f637231c","tid":1786462,"uid":119271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:21:13.000Z","msg":"我同意，平時都捐開星火立場，我真係想黃店有能力做落去先幫襯，所以有時會揀唔係捐錢既日子先去食<br />\n<br />\n同埋黃店relatively貴少少，但環境質素都好好多，希望餐廳手足頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee41b0dc1035b7419e56044312befd7ff9f639b7","tid":1786462,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d789895e238131d15c5f97328313a28b9f8ea016","tid":1786462,"uid":217413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"其實道理好簡單一句，點解我要花錢買難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔會幫襯藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"寧願唔買"},{"pid":"f35ad1bb3e8fad9b5daccac50307f05e744d9c2d","tid":1786462,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ba342f406704ec408be21b6c3113ceeb7842323","tid":1786462,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec9062da7be6e89dea30fc1d5bb6226e842db515","tid":1786462,"uid":130981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2f00c63eec158534fdcfc5a0d0c112eeee3b41cc","tid":1786462,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"試過食黃店，又貴又少，又唔係特別好食<br />\n又唔係特別裝修過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以無下次<br />\n呢d一定淘汰 ，無可能因為你黃而做傻仔<br />\n寧願唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望黃店爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:06:53.000Z","msg":"比人呃一兩次冇乜所謂<br />\n當買個教訓<br />\n黃藍